sequenceDiagram
    participant Scheduler as School Closing Scheduler
    participant Service as MonitoringService
    participant DAO as DeviceLogDAO / DeviceDAO
    participant DB as Relational Database
    participant Audit as AuditService

    Scheduler->>Service: runAutomaticLogout(10:00 PM)
    Service->>DAO: find devices still Inside
    DAO->>DB: SELECT open device_logs where campus_status = Inside
    DB-->>DAO: Open ingress records
    DAO-->>Service: Open ingress records
    Service->>Service: Set egress time to 10:00 PM
    Service->>DAO: Update logs and set campus_status Outside
    DAO->>DB: UPDATE device_logs auto_logged_out = true; UPDATE devices
    Service->>Audit: record automatic logout summary
